{"tid":1467940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷靜冷靜, 聽我講一講] 鬼可以捉, 但要處理恰當, 小心d唔好咬餌, 唔好成為自己唾罵既人, 香港人加油","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:51:24.000Z","uid":180905,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"53667863d525cb9668bae5ec61084ea0d8229462","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"先君子, 後小人<br />\n<br />\n講明我不割, 我都唔係冷氣軍師, 我今晚都11點半先走,<br />\n我係醫護, 昨, 今2日罷工出席, 唔好理我點罷法啦<br />\n此post希望大家冷靜認真檢討<br />\n<br />\n有打慣合作game既巴打, <br />\nLOL又好, 傳說對決又好, PUBG又好, OW又好<br />\n其實乜game只要係團戰, 其中一招好有效既就係出餌引敵人上釣, 4方8面都圍埋黎食曬佢<br />\n<br />\n今日機場就好放餌feel, 大陸仔, 假記者, 落單防暴等等<br />\n我唔係話大家捉鬼唔岩, <br />\n捉鬼岩, 你見到可疑既人就篤佢出黎, 大家再查證<br />\n捉錯既, 老虎蟹都要道歉, 捉岩既, 咪圍住佢唔比佢走囉<br />\n佢郁手既就名正言順綁佢囉, 但綁還綁, 都唔好綁到佢手充血丫, 綁太嚴重要節肢架<br />\n到時人地冇佐隻手, 你估真係以手還眼咩<br />\n女FA冇佐隻眼已經係事實, 以眼還眼係要警還, 要政府還, 但唔係個假記者還, 唔係要個大陸仔還<br />\n<br />\n個大陸仔上佐擔架, 再圍其實真係冇意思, 我知佢扮死呀, 但佢上得擔架, 就要當係病人, 我地冇權力冇能力去判佢係咪扮死<br />\n阻病人被救, 同班狗有乜分別, 佢上佐擔架就已經係揸住免死金牌, 搞唔過呀...<br />\n結果聽日大家都好欣賞既消防救護都會出黎話示威者...羸到乜野je<br />\n只會比人話係行私刑, 做緊自己最討厭既人架喳...<br />\n政府, 大陸, 藍絲又會有藉口抹黑, 何必呢...<br />\n<br />\n講番個落單警, 我睇番片, 佢真係比人打得好甘, 我明要救人, 我明先撩者賤<br />\n係班警犬搞事在先,<br />\n但記住, 佢地係有槍係身<br />\n當佢地真係覺得自己有生命威脅既時候會發生咩事?<br />\n到時佢真係名正言順架<br />\n利申, 我見隻狗比人搶棍打算轉頭, 完佐事腳仔都軟埋連爬帶滾, 我都睇到好爽,<br />\n但, 好危險呀...達到目的就要退, 比佢地增援到佐捉番住, 襲警又走唔甩架喇<br />\n<br />\n記住記住, 冷靜冷靜<br />\n1. 鬼可以捉, 但要適當處理, 第1件事一定唔係訴諸暴力, 你一開始自衛係合理, 但再追打落去就會變成行私刑<br />\n2. 救護唔阻得, 就算佢係狗佢係鬼都好, 人道理由, 一定要放, 唔好學對方做唔人道既野, 要話比全世界知, 不仁不義既係政府, 不人道既係黑警, 香港市民係智仁勇並存<br />\n3. 少不免, 除非救人, 都唔好同狗肉搏, 佢地full gear, 有武器, 肉搏一家係蝕, 救到人就好走, 唔好戀戰, 戀戰就會變送頭架喇<br />\n<br />\nsorry, 我理科出身, 文筆唔好, 組織能力又差, 1999, 希望大家明我想講咩, 歡迎討論, 我希望係善意討論, 唔同意都唔好話我割<br />\n我重申, 兄弟爬山, 各有各做, 但記住, 唔好成為自己唾罵緊既人, 停一停諗一諗<br />\n<br />\n我自己今日都係到諗, 究竟我地入機場要做既係乜野呢...<br />\n阻你飛定和你飛好呢...<br />\n我都知阻到經濟係好事, 係可以逼到幫狗官出黎回應, 但阻到旅客其實佢地都好無辜<br />\n機場滯留大家如果試過都知會好辛苦, 但阻到佢cancel flight我又好開心, 好矛盾<br />\nany肥, 我今日結果都係跟直覺去阻人飛, 希望係正面啦<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n黑警, 還眼<br />\n五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n香港人, 加油"},{"pid":"7d5e82450e8ec475063d64a08c4b38f0484bed25","tid":1467940,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"a99f1a5ff3e9a6bfd85449090d8bb391b5c04738","tid":1467940,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f19a130e790086c878b62fa34fa7edfead5327","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"自推X1<br />\n希望大家冷靜, 明白是非黑白, 黑警藍絲唔明, 我地要明<br />\n我地唔割, 但要識進步<br />\n要識知錯認錯改錯<br />\n<br />\n我地唔同佢垃圾政府唔知唔認唔改"},{"pid":"00fb989e014ab9dbd625ebfa57322155dc891b28","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"015474ca91908f0e16e8348ebc67f82d513daa37","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:26.000Z","msg":"希望大家冷靜, 明白是非黑白, 黑警藍絲唔明, 我地要明<br />\n我地唔割, 但要識進步<br />\n要識知錯認錯改錯"},{"pid":"f755a8575fd401dddf94a17ff2ea62093c21f21c","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:49.000Z","msg":"希望大家睇到, 我再繼續推"},{"pid":"0b699e18d826948e71e1f3480c7e9879616698fc","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:09.000Z","msg":"錯咪錯囉, 理解自己錯乜野, 唔好重覆犯錯<br />\n錯佐我都唔撚割呀, 一齊加油move on 呀"},{"pid":"fa1764d285516734a73d8dde632157a252f9cd7c","tid":1467940,"uid":190700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKH32ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKH32ot.jpg&h=5e099b86&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYUh6P8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYUh6P8.jpg&h=8cec500b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVxLwho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVxLwho.jpg&h=415b935b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d79744263ab90c0c84d2d810c28f2bc8d3fe728d","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa1764d285516734a73d8dde632157a252f9cd7c","tid":1467940,"uid":190700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKH32ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKH32ot.jpg&h=5e099b86&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYUh6P8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYUh6P8.jpg&h=8cec500b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVxLwho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVxLwho.jpg&h=415b935b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"岩呀, 多謝巴打認同"},{"pid":"a02a1c0f952898ee41cd50d9f607867b53ef0b38","tid":1467940,"uid":238197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"［事後檢討］今日捉鬼事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467998</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同意手足<br />\n覺得今日大家都好緊張"},{"pid":"4f0f5582688520f2545d62ff797bb92375431e91","tid":1467940,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"Well said<br />\n<br />\n有勇有謀，收放自如，知進退，不慍不火"},{"pid":"6ad0f1396efd54112e17ba05e4c65539ded52116","tid":1467940,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾句建議姐818 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各自爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多手足受傷 被捕 點解我地仲企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因 為 未 完 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818見</span>"},{"pid":"658fe27bbd9529b2925251ee4205cc44fd44af50","tid":1467940,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:11.000Z","msg":"直接唔捉 每次捉都有事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42134b95cd3ce76bdb8328bc8aabba2c399c6801","tid":1467940,"uid":304622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"push，樓主正解"},{"pid":"0c54ed48704cd808a71156183ee8a59bded9eb3e","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658fe27bbd9529b2925251ee4205cc44fd44af50","tid":1467940,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:11.000Z","msg":"直接唔捉 每次捉都有事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"篤出黎比大家小心都好<br />\n但佢唔郁手就唔好綁, 下下都綁又會比人話未審先判<br />\n我地綁, 係為佐唔比佢傷人, 要出師有名"},{"pid":"a87458d38ab91e52539cdd06d5faad33023c8537","tid":1467940,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"捉到鬼最緊要搵證據<br />\n而唔係打佢<br />\n搵到證據就叫記者<br />\n跟住？<br />\n除鳩哂佢d衫掉佢出馬路 自自然然會有人執佢"},{"pid":"b983df6ef2ab87e4867b3f4cc8f5d9dc3e7c8e0b","tid":1467940,"uid":245230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88d0494cd92cf35f2c3fad066abe38e074ed3954","tid":1467940,"uid":281488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"啱啱發夢入左鬼城，<br />\n夢中深深感覺到，好多天師手足想捉鬼，反而變得人心遑遑。但亦反映到鬼顯然想天師之間割裂，互相懷疑！<br />\n夢中兩隻鬼都太蠢太易捉，有隻重要扮記者，袋住件大同小異嘅藍tee ，對鏡頭笑，明顯想刺激群眾情緒，而周圍好多難分真與假嘅手足，<br />\n當住記者面前發表好多過激言論甚至動手，<br />\n我所知嘅衝衝派天師先冇咁衝動同激動，<br />\n更進一步令大家疑心生暗鬼，正中對方下懷。<br />\n大家可以好似手足講咁完全唔理，<br />\n唔捉就唔會引起衝突同懷疑！<br />\n但考慮到誘餌鬼亦可能主動現身挑釁，<br />\n因此，大家亦可以考慮進一步手段，<br />\n一方面可以釋除大家互相懷疑嘅疑慮，另一方面大家統一地知道面對同樣情況應該點做，而唔會出現分歧同亂成一團。<br />\n既然大家都知有餌，又可能有不停刺激氣氛既鬼，真係到要對付鬼時，方法就變得簡單得多：<br />\n我地光明正大，鬼就唔同。<br />\n所以，我地需要一個放下身段，互相檢視嘅流程：<br />\n<br />\n1.如被天師手足懷疑，勿衝動，保持冷靜，並確保在公眾環境同有大量手足在場時，主動提供身份証明文件(工作證、學生證等)俾天師手足去check 同解釋釋疑，再念驅邪咒語&ldquo;克竟荃加筆德好死！&rdquo;，此時搜身天師不得記錄任何對方嘅資訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.搜身天師搜完人，發現誤會當然定要向對方真誠道歉(據我所知鬼既職業係嚟識向人道歉)，而對方亦有權向天師核實個人身份，咁就更公平，同唔怕有鬼亂扮人去搜人身<br />\n<br />\n3.如遇不合作者，先由同性人士封鎖行動，但唔行其他私刑，呼叫記者，並在記者或有旁人紀錄嘅情況場下，鏡頭下翻查其隨身物件同銀包証件<br />\n<br />\n3.過程盡量溫和，同時唔可以一開始就公開証件資料，以防私人資訊外流，直到搵到對方係鬼既關鍵証據<br />\n<br />\n5.以上情況發生時，旁人不起哄，不發表任何傷人或刺激性言論，否則以懷疑鬼既方式處理，搜袋同銀包証件<br />\n<br />\n如果發現係鬼機會極高，<br />\n我建議交由記者記下佢所有個人資訊，並將鬼交俾記者處理。<br />\n我地無需要行私刑，因為，我地每次以文明既表現捉到一隻鬼，我地就多一分，向公眾証明鬼城手段幾咁低劣，顯示我地同佢地嘅不同。<br />\n而大家亦盡量唔好攜帶太私隱或會引起懷疑的物件，以免產生不必要誤會。<br />\n<br />\n再補充返，<br />\n大家首先就係唔好諗捉鬼，<br />\n以上既流程係當有d 誘餌鬼做得太過份太挑釁時，一d 預先考慮好既應對方式。<br />\n畢竟我地唔知鬼會唔會主動挑釁，<br />\n起碼大家心底知道萬一真係有鬼明顯地出現，或者有戰友被鬼騷擾發動左捉鬼行動時，應該點進行統一、清晰、文明、對大家有利無害既行動。<br />\n我個人更希望大家唔需要做到，但有個共識既back up plan 總安全d。<br />\n<br />\n以上內容都係我啱啱瞓醒時嘅夢話，行唔行得通完全唔知，亦希望冇需要用到！只係有備無患預先確立一個共識，歡迎大家改動同補完！"},{"pid":"24f803bb83848e412af011bd4cc640d315d150a9","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a87458d38ab91e52539cdd06d5faad33023c8537","tid":1467940,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"捉到鬼最緊要搵證據<br />\n而唔係打佢<br />\n搵到證據就叫記者<br />\n跟住？<br />\n除鳩哂佢d衫掉佢出馬路 自自然然會有人執佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"屌, 除衫笑撚佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵記者就好ok喇, 除衫我當你講笑算<br />\nhaha"},{"pid":"2a6dc342e307d0ec56cf5c3349c5e90222893d79","tid":1467940,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c54ed48704cd808a71156183ee8a59bded9eb3e","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658fe27bbd9529b2925251ee4205cc44fd44af50","tid":1467940,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:11.000Z","msg":"直接唔捉 每次捉都有事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"篤出黎比大家小心都好<br />\n但佢唔郁手就唔好綁, 下下都綁又會比人話未審先判<br />\n我地綁, 係為佐唔比佢傷人, 要出師有名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔好再捉鬼喇 隻鬼最想做既就係你地捉住佢 跟住就挑釁你打佢 你一出手佢地就已經達成目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb32f3a73d42030927e335afb653912cb60c01e","tid":1467940,"uid":8584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"7692743ef838e6e9ad9f65e7e156bf19f9531d3d","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6dc342e307d0ec56cf5c3349c5e90222893d79","tid":1467940,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c54ed48704cd808a71156183ee8a59bded9eb3e","tid":1467940,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislik